{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Server-sent events","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events\">Server-sent events</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>指南</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events/Using_server-sent_events\">Using server-sent events</a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>接口</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventSource\"><code>EventSource</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>一个网页获取新的数据通常需要发送一个请求到服务器，也就是向服务器请求的页面。使用 server-sent 事件，服务器可以在任何时刻向我们的 Web 页面推送数据和信息。这些被推送进来的信息可以在这个页面上作为 <em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\">Events</a> + data</em> 的形式来处理。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概念与使用","title":"概念与使用","isH3":false,"content":"<p>可以前往我们这篇文章 《<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events/Using_server-sent_events\">使用“server-sent event”</a>》学习怎么使用 server-sent 事件。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"接口","title":"接口","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"eventsource\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventSource\"><code>EventSource</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Defines all the features that handle connecting to a server, receiving events/data, errors, closing a connection, etc.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/dom-examples/tree/master/server-sent-events\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Simple SSE demo using PHP</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/server-sent-events.html#server-sent-events","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"undefined"}},{